1
00:01:03,710 --> 00:01:05,880
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:09,880
[Episode 14]

3
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:14,240
I want you to go to the palace
and beg His Majesty

4
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:16,640
to make you his concubine!

5
00:01:18,230 --> 00:01:19,000
Go!

6
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:21,880
Come with me!

7
00:01:35,350 --> 00:01:37,150
How is it you? Shouldn't you be...

8
00:01:37,150 --> 00:01:38,150
Surprised?

9
00:01:38,590 --> 00:01:39,789
My bride.

10
00:01:40,150 --> 00:01:41,509
I've come for you.

11
00:01:52,890 --> 00:01:54,490
My Lady, run!

12
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:55,310
Xi'er!

13
00:01:55,430 --> 00:01:58,160
Such deep loyalty
between mistress and servant.

14
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:14,800
Go ahead, run.

15
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,310
Don't worry, Li.

16
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,680
After you're gone,

17
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,400
I will surely make this girl

18
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:25,079
suffer terribly.

19
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:25,870
No!

20
00:02:25,870 --> 00:02:27,360
Xi'er. No!

21
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,960
My Lady, run!

22
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:29,680
Shut up!

23
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:35,800
Take me away. I'll go with you.

24
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,960
If you sincerely beg me,

25
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:43,280
I can let her go.

26
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:46,750
But when you're begging me,

27
00:02:47,630 --> 00:02:49,310
what should you call me?

28
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:59,030
Please, husband,

29
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,310
release Xi'er.

30
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,430
Too quiet.

31
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:06,910
I can't hear you.

32
00:03:10,090 --> 00:03:13,310
I beg you, my husband, to release Xi'er.

33
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,079
All right.

34
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,470
However,

35
00:03:18,470 --> 00:03:19,840
it's not sincere.

36
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:24,190
My Lady, don't be afraid.

37
00:03:29,870 --> 00:03:31,120
Xi'er!

38
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,280
Xi'er!

39
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,190
Xi'er.

40
00:03:39,820 --> 00:03:40,940
Xi'er.

41
00:03:44,710 --> 00:03:45,870
Xi'er.

42
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,420
Xi'er.

43
00:03:53,310 --> 00:03:54,630
Did you see that?

44
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:57,960
You killed her.

45
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,360
Just wait.

46
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:07,360
I'll make you pay with your life!

47
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,030
Who's there?

48
00:04:17,790 --> 00:04:19,260
Traitor Xun Simo,

49
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:21,190
release Miss Jiang immediately!

50
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,510
A dog of Xie Jiuzhao—

51
00:04:26,530 --> 00:04:28,260
how loud you bark.

52
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,000
I want to see

53
00:04:30,310 --> 00:04:32,350
if you can actually bite.

54
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:38,040
[Moonlit Spectacle]

55
00:04:42,630 --> 00:04:45,120
Jiuzhao, why did you invite me
to the Imperial Garden?

56
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:47,630
You're not asking me
to appreciate flowers, are you?

57
00:04:47,630 --> 00:04:48,920
Twelve years ago,

58
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:51,600
if I hadn't been taken away,

59
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,930
the one sitting on the throne today

60
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,310
might have been you, Nianzhao.

61
00:04:58,950 --> 00:04:59,080
You are destined to rule.

62
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:00,750
[Moonlit Spectacle]

63
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:02,070
I respect and love you,

64
00:05:02,070 --> 00:05:03,750
and have never harbored
any treasonous thoughts.

65
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:04,630
Besides,

66
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,040
as long as you're here,

67
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:11,440
you'll always look after me, your brother.

68
00:05:15,870 --> 00:05:17,000
Don't overthink it.

69
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,830
It was just a passing thought.

70
00:05:20,190 --> 00:05:20,950
Yes.

71
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:24,510
The traitor Xun Simo escaped last night.

72
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:26,720
Stay within the palace these days

73
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,950
to avoid any mishaps.

74
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:32,510
How dare Xun Simo be so brazen!

75
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:34,510
He must not be spared this time.

76
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,159
Jiuzhao.

77
00:05:38,510 --> 00:05:40,159
I believe...

78
00:05:41,190 --> 00:05:43,650
I believe Mother has
nothing to do with this.

79
00:05:43,870 --> 00:05:45,070
I humbly request

80
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:48,440
that you not direct
your anger toward Mother.

81
00:05:52,710 --> 00:05:55,600
[Moonlit Spectacle]

82
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,240
Nianzhao.

83
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:03,050
If you still consider me your brother,

84
00:06:03,970 --> 00:06:06,210
then stay out of this matter.

85
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:17,920
My Lady.

86
00:06:18,630 --> 00:06:19,680
My Lady.

87
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,270
My Lady.

88
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,240
My Lady.

89
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,800
Li, wake up.

90
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:27,560
Xi'er.

91
00:06:29,310 --> 00:06:29,950
Mother.

92
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,480
Li.

93
00:06:32,350 --> 00:06:33,150
Li.

94
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,270
Xi'er.

95
00:06:50,180 --> 00:06:50,860
General.

96
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,480
Darn it!

97
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:03,030
Who told you to touch her?

98
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:04,360
Please calm down, General.

99
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,560
Miss Jiang kept resisting,

100
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,720
so I had no choice...

101
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:08,250
Please calm down, General.

102
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:15,190
Take him away.

103
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:16,300
Yes, General.

104
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,360
Li,

105
00:07:27,020 --> 00:07:28,750
I'm sorry you were frightened.

106
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,270
It was their fault.

107
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:31,760
Seeing you like this

108
00:07:32,159 --> 00:07:33,630
breaks my heart too.

109
00:07:36,990 --> 00:07:38,480
Xun Simo.

110
00:07:40,950 --> 00:07:42,800
You make me sick.

111
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:53,510
Don't come any closer.

112
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:54,360
Stay back.

113
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,240
Li,

114
00:07:57,430 --> 00:07:58,720
you can't do this.

115
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,770
Xie Jiuzhao isn't here yet,

116
00:08:01,510 --> 00:08:03,250
so you can't die now.

117
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:09,800
You're willing to kill yourself for him?

118
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,950
Do you love Xie Jiuzhao that much?

119
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,920
Don't be delusional.

120
00:08:15,590 --> 00:08:17,100
Xie Jiuzhao

121
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:19,610
won't come.

122
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:28,280
You just don't want him
to come and die, right?

123
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:30,780
Fine, let's wait and see.

124
00:08:38,630 --> 00:08:39,440
Report!

125
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:45,390
How did it go?

126
00:08:45,390 --> 00:08:46,190
Your Majesty,

127
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,840
I have failed your mission.

128
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,390
I beg for your punishment.

129
00:08:50,390 --> 00:08:51,270
Say no more.

130
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:53,010
Go tend to your wounds now.

131
00:08:53,150 --> 00:08:54,150
Where is Jiang Li?

132
00:08:57,870 --> 00:08:58,630
Dismissed.

133
00:08:58,630 --> 00:08:59,690
Yes, Your Majesty.

134
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,000
Where is she?

135
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:04,850
Miss Jiang

136
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,910
is in Xun Simo's hands.

137
00:09:09,670 --> 00:09:10,840
Where are they?

138
00:09:14,550 --> 00:09:15,550
Speak up!

139
00:09:15,870 --> 00:09:16,670
Your Majesty,

140
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:19,000
if I tell you,

141
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:21,670
I would be the greatest traitor
in the Great Zhao State.

142
00:09:21,670 --> 00:09:23,470
Are you deceiving your emperor?

143
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,940
I consider you my brother.

144
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:27,600
Must I beg you?

145
00:09:30,650 --> 00:09:32,680
Xun Simo sent a message.

146
00:09:33,790 --> 00:09:35,960
He wants you to go
to Chunliu Garden alone.

147
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:36,750
Otherwise,

148
00:09:37,750 --> 00:09:39,910
Miss Jiang's life will be in danger.

149
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:45,040
Your Majesty!

150
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,890
This is surely a trap.

151
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,320
I dare to suggest

152
00:09:48,340 --> 00:09:49,850
that you reconsider for a moment

153
00:09:49,850 --> 00:09:51,310
and find a safer approach.

154
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:53,720
I have made up my mind.

155
00:09:54,630 --> 00:09:56,150
If you try to stop me again,

156
00:09:56,710 --> 00:09:58,710
our relationship will be over.

157
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,120
Your Majesty!

158
00:10:02,030 --> 00:10:02,840
Guards!

159
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:05,510
Take the commander away
to treat his wounds.

160
00:10:05,510 --> 00:10:06,870
After he recovers,

161
00:10:07,150 --> 00:10:10,010
exile him to Suzhou
and conscript him into the army!

162
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:12,270
I

163
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:15,270
never want to see you again.

164
00:10:22,510 --> 00:10:24,320
Jiuzhao, you cannot go!

165
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:25,560
Get out of my way.

166
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,960
You are the ruler of a nation.

167
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,440
You must not be bewitched by a woman

168
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,260
and lose your judgment.

169
00:10:29,260 --> 00:10:30,320
I told you

170
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,630
not to interfere anymore.

171
00:10:31,630 --> 00:10:32,380
Have you forgotten?

172
00:10:32,380 --> 00:10:34,490
If you insist on rescuing Miss Jiang,

173
00:10:34,550 --> 00:10:36,550
then let me take men to do it instead.

174
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:37,750
Please trust me.

175
00:10:37,750 --> 00:10:39,080
Why should I trust you?

176
00:10:39,290 --> 00:10:40,750
If anything happens to her,

177
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:42,680
can you bear that responsibility?

178
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:44,910
Jiuzhao.

179
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:48,000
Please prioritize the empire

180
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,960
and your people.

181
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,750
The empire and the people

182
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:53,550
don't conflict with saving her.

183
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:56,720
There have been
many wise rulers throughout history,

184
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,480
but Jiang Li only has me.

185
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,510
Please don't go!

186
00:10:59,790 --> 00:11:01,030
I don't want you to go.

187
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:06,150
If you truly care about me,

188
00:11:06,750 --> 00:11:08,150
after I leave the palace,

189
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,600
don't do anything rash.

190
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:15,600
Really?

191
00:11:17,030 --> 00:11:17,910
Jiuzhao.

192
00:11:19,310 --> 00:11:20,430
Is this

193
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:23,440
your final choice?
